{"tid":1040692,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［勁量！渾身是勁！］勁量摺機 Energizer Power Max P8100s","createTime":"2019-02-28T09:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T06:29:58.000Z","uid":2104,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3211708f0a37ecd89f011f53a81da7630ba00c","tid":1040692,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"勁量 Energizer 早前推出過一款大得像磚頭的智能手機 Power Max P18K Pop，擁有 18,000mAh 電池，號稱可連續播放 48 小時影片。而除了那部大牛龜之外，勁量繼續發佈一款可摺疊的手機 Power Max P8100S，它在翻開的狀態下最大可展現8吋熒幕，更支援 5G 新一代流動網絡。<br />\n<br />\n這部手機的摺疊式設計跟 Samsung Galaxy Fold 相似，同樣是內反式設計，「封面」是一個解像度為 2,160 x 1080 的 6 吋大熒幕，而攤開之後裡面就是另一個 8.1 吋大的熒幕，該熒幕解像度達到 2,048 x 1,536。<br />\n<br />\n電量方面，雖然沒有早前推出的兄弟機 Power Max P18K Pop 多，只有 10,000mAh，不過已經比大部份智能手機還要多，當然也是可摺疊智能手機當中，最多電量的一款。而它使用 USB Type-C 插口，可支援 18W 快速充電。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDgTHFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDgTHFE.png&h=91f0f3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvibukF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvibukF.png&h=f03fa982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於硬件配置，Power Max P8100S 搭載 Snapdragon 855 處理器、8GB RAM 與 256GB ROM，另外支援 microSD 擴充容量。內置有 2,400 萬像素感光元件的前置鏡頭，以及 4,800 萬像素＋1,200 萬像素感光元件的雙主鏡頭相機。搭載了 Android 9 Pie 作業系統。此機未來將會推出支援 5G 網絡的型號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0QncdNq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0QncdNq.png&h=f11ab438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過在 MWC 2019 展覽當中，這部 Power Max P8100S 只放在玻璃飾櫃裡給大家拍照，仍未能給到場者拿上手。售價方面，據稱將會以 850 歐元（約HK$7,592）的價格推出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQfJksu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQfJksu.png&h=2c258e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勁量應該會蠃在血統上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45181a8040e5a1c4b0b263c1028d94eff4cbd3f3","tid":1040692,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"出處<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/28/power-max-p8100s/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F28%2Fpower-max-p8100s%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=6e652f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/28/power-max-p8100s/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"c0bef42a4070cac17616272f696bca4f242a06db","tid":1040692,"uid":2777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2f7e97de961f114ea586757263d076f0485ec89","tid":1040692,"uid":15564,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"摺mon變公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5763a46701d41c9355b8586cf0e8b02c44ddae1a","tid":1040692,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f7e97de961f114ea586757263d076f0485ec89","tid":1040692,"uid":15564,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"摺mon變公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"個個都等Samsung 出手先"},{"pid":"0af65d250c896565a1ac0db11002562529465555","tid":1040692,"uid":35233,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"sansung 華為 勁量<br />\n三部入面samsung 部野最7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8dac5a0b8e02a427b000c35c7f2f739569b908","tid":1040692,"uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"又平又核電<br />\n邊個話新技術要包容下貴？<br />\n出多一個禮拜就變舊技術啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下個月應該5000樓下就有"},{"pid":"b24db5390f6c0d83787477ed3865dc58625e4933","tid":1040692,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"7千"},{"pid":"02f3c5202f75a2